stencil_223.name: Wires
stencil_223.desc: Various wires used in electrical circuit design for usages in CAD software to allow users to quickly make electrical schematics

stencil_224.name: JIC / NFPA Symbols
stencil_224.desc: Standard electrical JIC / NFPA symbols used to represent contactors, thermal overloads, motors and transformers for usage in electrical schematic diagrams

stencil_225.name: IEC Symbols
stencil_225.desc: Standard electrical IEC symbols also known as IEC 60617 (British Standard BS 3939) used to represent various devices including pilot lights, relays, timers and switches for usage in electrical schematic diagrams

stencil_226.name: Electronic Symbols
stencil_226.desc: Standard electronic symbols used to represent various devices such as resistors, transistors, batteries, capacitors and inductors for usage in electronic diagrams

stencil_227.name: IEC Power, Meters, Transformers, Motors
stencil_227.desc: Electrical IEC symbols (IEC 60617 / BS 3939) used to represent transformers, motors and meters for usage in electrical schematic diagrams

stencil_228.name: IEC Isolators, Disconnectors, Fuses, Contactors, Overloads
stencil_228.desc: Electrical IEC 60617 / BS 3939 symbols representing isolators, disconnectors, fuses,cContactors and overloads for usage in drawing electrical circuits

stencil_229.name: Single Line Symbols
stencil_229.desc: Single line symbols electrical symbols used to represent various electrical devices for usages in electrical schematic design

stencil_230.name: Layout
stencil_230.desc: Panel layout symbols used in electrical schematics to denote the layout of various components in an electrical panel

stencil_231.name: Layout 3D
stencil_231.desc: 3D Panel Layout symbols used in electrical schematics to represent front panel display and layout

stencil_232.name: Pneumatic Pumps, Cylinders and Motors
stencil_232.desc: Pneumatic pumps, cylinders and motor symbols used in the design of pneumatic circuit drawings

stencil_233.name: Pneumatic Valves
stencil_233.desc: Pneumatic valves symbols including 3/2 ways, 5/2 ways and other devices used in the design of pneumatic circuit drawings

stencil_234.name: Pneumatic Misc
stencil_234.desc: Miscellaneous pneumatic symbols and devices used in pneumatic circuit design

stencil_235.name: Hydraulic Misc
stencil_235.desc: Miscellaneous hydraulic symbols and devices used in hydraulic circuit design

stencil_236.name: Hydraulic Valves
stencil_236.desc: Hydraulic valves symbols including 3/2 ways, 5/2 ways and other devices used in the design of hydraulic circuit drawings

stencil_237.name: Hydraulic Pumps, Cylinders and Motors
stencil_237.desc: Hydraulic pumps, cylinders and motor symbols used in the design of hydraulic circuit drawings

stencil_49.name: Measurement tools
stencil_49.desc: Measurement symbols used in design of electrical, pneumatic and hydraulic circuits

stencil_51.name: Title blocks
